&#x2022	Join Indian Navy Are Released for Executive Sports & Law Branch Entry Recruitment Indian Navy Vacancies.
 •	Candidate Can Apply Between 13/01/2023 to 28/01/2023.
 •	Candidate Read the Notification Before Apply the Recruitment Application Form in Indian Navy Executive Sports & Law June 2023 Course Recruitment 2023..
•	Kindly Check and Collect the All Document - Eligibility, ID Proof, Address Details, Basic Details.
•	Kindly Ready Scan Document Related to Recruitment Form - Photo, Sign, ID Proof, Etc.
Before Submit the Application Form Must Check the Preview and All Columns Carefully.
No Application Fees in Indian Navy Recruitment But. Candidate Must Final Submit the Form.
Take A Print Out of Final Submitted Form
job_eligibility_by_education: For Air Force and Naval Wings - Passing Certification of Class 12th exam with Physics and Mathematics
